{"text": "This modern, designer-furnished 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina features views of the Little Fatra and Martinky. The layout of the apartment is ideal for those who want to enjoy the benefits of a high position without overheating or needing air conditioning. The living room has access to a balcony that runs the entire width of the living room, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The bedroom is furnished with a double bed and nightstands, while the children's room serves as an office. The bathroom features a bidet shower by the toilet and underfloor electric heating for quick ventilation when needed."}
